recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a medium saucepan. Add chicken and mushroom and cook, stirring frequently, for 4 minutes or until golden. Add vegetables and stock or water, cover and simmer for 10 minutes or until vegetables are very soft and chicken is cooked through.
